null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":2048,"height":1152,"file_path":"/osM8EfETpL8VbtCJKmA5PDQeOk7.jpg","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/re2S8BsdWa2NcPxFEy62z4MADsF.jpg","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/8TRYjopIQq1ZoBS28MkzsAmbeSQ.jpg","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1916,"height":1078,"file_path":"/hnIXAkBXJmNkxfJ2H8hUBTID1Sp.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1916,"height":1078,"file_path":"/1ey5LnGjCX6XZYSY21XJNdKdxyL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1916,"height":1078,"file_path":"/kIpGyPLXCVZsUTp42KXc6Dnq4JO.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1916,"height":1078,"file_path":"/zh8qkBHhwy87qXi0a0T1EBEHjph.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1916,"height":1078,"file_path":"/oRrc5LY5mirHblp8Ry2Y3YQHAt4.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T05:32:50.03+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"Elite Squad: The Enemy Within","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"http://www.tropa2.com.br/","overview":"After a bloody invasion of the BOPE in the High-Security Penitentiary Bangu 1 in Rio de Janeiro to control a rebellion of interns, the Lieutenant-Colonel Roberto Nascimento and the second in command Captain André Matias are accused by the Human Right Aids member Diogo Fraga of execution of prisoners. Matias is transferred to the corrupted Military Police and Nascimento is exonerated from the BOPE by the Governor."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"Tropa de Elite 2","runtime":115,"tagline":"O Inimigo Agora é Outro","homepage":"","overview":"Nascimento enfrenta um novo inimigo: as milícias. Ao bater de frente com o sistema que domina o Rio de Janeiro, ele descobre que o problema é muito maior do que imaginava. E não é só. Ele precisa equilibrar o desafio de pacificar uma cidade ocupada pelo crime com as constantes preocupações com o filho adolescente. Quando o universo pessoal e o profissional de Nascimento se encontram, o resultado é explosivo."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"精英部队2：大敌当前","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"　　在上一集的故事结束后13年,巴西里约特别警察行动部队队长纳西门托的个人和家庭生活成为了《精英部队2》的主线。里约特别警察行动在一次平复监狱暴动的行动中吃了大亏,伤了元气。队长纳西门托虽然平步青云,但也因为这次事件的影响受到了牵连。这时候,一场大规模的政治斗争在巴西的土地上燃烧开来,上至总统贵族,下至贩夫走卒,统统都受到了影响。不仅仅是警察局、连军队和特别警察部门都惹了麻烦。不过,对于纳西门托来说,他不仅有外患,而且还有内忧。他的正值青春期的孩子渐渐脱离了纳西门托的监管,跑到了里约热内卢的街头,做了一个小混混。他的这种行为,直接对他的继父产生了巨大的影响。在这个年龄,在这样的一个国家,纳西门托要如何才能安身立命,要如何才能安稳地活下去?"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Efter en blodig invasion af BOPE i High-Security Penitentiary Bangu en i Rio de Janeiro til at styre en opstand i praktikanter ...Efter en blodig invasion af BOPE i High-Security Penitentiary Bangu en i Rio de Janeiro til at styre en opstand i praktikanter, er oberstløjtnant Roberto Nascimento og næstkommanderende kaptajn André Matias anklaget af Human Right Aids medlem Diogo Fraga af henrettelse af fanger. Matias er overført til militærpolitiet og korrumperet Nascimento er fritaget fra BOPE, som guvernør. Men på grund af den stigende popularitet af Nascimento, Guvernøren opfordrer ham til at hold op med intelligens område af Secretary of Security. Langs år, er Fraga, der er gift med Nascimento tidligere hustru, valgte State Representative og Nascimento søn Rafael har problemer med sin biologiske far. I mellemtiden Nascimento og BOPE fordrive narkohandlere fra flere slumkvarterer udste men en anden fjende."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Özel Tim 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rio de Janeiro tarihinin en büyük kıyımı olmuştu. Böyle olduğu halde sistem hala yerinde duruyordu. Sistem kolunu kurtarmak için elini feda eder. Sistem kendini yeniden düzenler, yeni bir etki yaratır. Yeni bir lider yaratır * Efsane devam ediyor. Acımasız, katı, kanlı, yoz ve hızlı bu film, tartışmalı ve popüler Özel Tim’in devamı niteliğinde ve neredeyse aynı kadroyla çekilmiş. Brezilya’da tüm zamanların hasılat rekorunu kıran film, hikâyeyi Roberto Nascimento’nun yarbaylığa yükseldiği on üç yıl sonrasına taşıyor. Roberto bir hapishane isyanını iyi idare edemediği için işinden olduysa da sonunda bir hükümet istihbarat mevkisine atanır; fakat şimdi de Emniyet Genel Müdürlüğü, eyalet valisi, askeri polis ve paramiliter gruplar arasındaki kanlı bir çekişmenin tam ortasına düşmüştür."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Elite Squad: Im Sumpf der Korruption","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Zehn Jahre ist es her, dass Capitão Nascimento ein Einsatzkommando der BOPE, DIE Elitetruppe der brasilianischen Militärpolizei, anführte, um für den damals anstehend Papst-Besuch zumindest zeitweilig für etwas Ruhe und Ordnung zu sorgen. Inzwischen leitet Nascimento die BOPE und kann bereits auf einige Erfolge im Kampf gegen die Drogenmafia zurückblicken. Während die Kriminellen der Stadt jedoch meist ein klares Ziel abgeben, muss Nascimento mehr und mehr auch gegen einen neuen Feind kämpfen, einen Feind aus den eigenen Reihen: Korrupte Polizisten und Politiker versuchen die Machtspiele der unterschiedlichen kriminellen Gruppierungen für ihre eigenen Zwecke zu nutzen und gehen dabei bis zum Äußersten."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Tropa de elite 2 - Il nemico ora è un altro","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Il capitano Roberto Nascimento viene promosso a capo dell'intelligence militare, mentre l'ufficiale Matias lo sostituisce al comando del BOPE, la squadra speciale che opera nel difficile scenario delle favelas brasiliane."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Troupe d'Élite : l'Ennemi Intérieur","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Le colonel Nascimento est chargé de maîtriser une émeute dans l’une des prisons les plus violentes du Brésil où trois gangs sont en guerre ouverte. Les forces de la BOPE (Bataillon des opérations spéciales de police) sont contraintes d'accepter l'intervention d'un intermédiaire : un activiste politique qui est sensé calmer les tensions entre les émeutiers et la police. Cependant, la situation dégénère rapidement et tourne à la prise d'otage pour déboucher sur un véritable carnage. Démis de ses fonctions, Nascimento est nommé à un secrétariat d’État. Il va alors découvrir à quel point la corruption règne aux plus hauts niveaux de l’Etat."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Elitarni: Ostatnie starcie","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sequel pierwszej części opowiada nam o przestępczości i handlu narkotykami w favelach - lokalnych slumsach Rio de Janeiro - mieście, w którym policja wydaje się nie mieć prawa głosu. Podpułkownik Nascimento (Wagner Moura) jest nadal dowódcą BOPE - elitarnej brazylijskiej jednostki policji do zadań specjalnych, a jego prawą ręką jest kapitan André Matias (André Ramiro). W świecie bez zasad, po dwóch stronach barykady stoją oddziały specjalne, gdzie milicja walczy z bezwzględnymi bossami ulicznych gangów oraz z korupcją i żądnymi władzy politykami."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Tropa de Elite 2","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Rio De Janeiros största problem är inte längre knarkhandeln i favelorna, utan korruptionen som genomsyrar polisväsendet och som sträcker sig högt upp i Brasiliens maktväsende. Löjtnant Nascimento inser att detta problem inte kan lösas med våld, utan med politik. Hans fiender är inte längre gatans slödder, utan högt uppsatta tjänsteman som visar sig vara långt mycket farligare. När familjen distanserar sig från Nascimento och hans fiender finns bland hans egna så står han allt ensammare i kampen för rättvisa."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"Элитный отряд: Враг внутри","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Элитный отряд показал себя весьма эффективным средством борьбы с наркокартелями, перекрыв кислород организованной преступности и разгромив несколько банд. Но тут совершенно неожиданно силы правопорядка начинают терпеть одно поражение за другим."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Tropa de élite 2","runtime":116,"tagline":"El enemigo ahora es otro.","homepage":"","overview":"Después de un altercado en prisión, el excapitán Nascimento, ahora oficial de seguridad de alto rango en Río de Janeiro, se ve envuelto en una sangrienta disputa política que involucra a oficiales del gobierno y grupos paramilitares."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Het verhaal speelt zich 13 jaar na het eerste deel af. Kapitein Nascimento wordt geconfronteerd met nieuwe vijanden: de milities, corrupte politieagenten die zich opdringen bij de bevolking van de sloppenwijken."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Elitní jednotka 2: Vnitřní nepřítel","runtime":116,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nascimento, velitel policejní jednotky BOPE v Riu de Janeiru, krvavě potlačí vzpouru ve věznici pro nebezpečné zločince. Je zbaven své funkce, i když se mu podařilo vyhnat z městských slumů většinu drogových dealerů. Jejich místa však zabírá zkorumpovaná policie a Nascimento se rozhodne zasáhnout. (MFF Cinema Mundi)"},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Eliittijoukot 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Edettyään urallaan BOPE-joukkojen komentaja Nascimiento näkee todellisen vihollisensa: maansa ryvettyneen tilan, jossa kaikki on ostettavissa."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Elit halálosztók 2.","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nascimento rendőrfőnök lelkesen végzi munkáját, hogy megtisztítsa az utcákat a bűnözéstől. Amikor politikusi karriert kínálnak neki, örömmel vállalja, mert úgy gondolja, így majd többet tehet. Azonban hamarosan rájön, hogy csupán eltávolítani akarták az útból, hogy ne akadályozza egyes bűnöző körök utcai érdekeit."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Μετά την αιματοβαμμένη εισβολή στην φαβέλα Μπανγκού του Ρίο, ο αστυνόμος Ρομπέρτο Νασιμέντο κι ο υπαρχηγός Αντρές Ματίας κατηγορούνται από μέλος του οργανισμού ανθρωπίνων δικαιωμάτων. Ο Ματίας μεταφέρεται στη διεφθαρμένη στρατιωτική αστυνομία, ενώ ο Νασιμέντο απαλλάσσεται από τις υπηρεσίες του. Όμως, ο Νασιμέντο έχει γίνει λαοφιλής και τον καλούν στην μυστική υπηρεσία του υπουργείου ασφαλείας."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"יחידת עילית 2: אוייב מבית","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"הסרט הברזילאי הטוב ביותר לשנת 2010 סיפורם של הקולונל רוברטו נאסימנטו וקפטן אנדרה מתיאס ומאבקם בשחיתות הגואה במשטרה הצבאית של ברזיל. כאשר ניסיון השתלטות על מרד אסירים בכלא משתבש והופך את הקריירות של שניהם. החל מרגע זה חייהם ישתנו לנצח"},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Trupa de Elită 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Tropa de Elite 2: O Inimigo Agora é Outro","runtime":115,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"O destino da cidade do Rio de Janeiro e de Nascimento se cruzam em \"Tropa de Elite 2\", quando suas obrigações de pai se chocam com as de policial. Mais maduro, estratégico e solitário, o agora Coronel Nascimento faz o bope crescer e coloca o tráfico de drogas de joelho. Isto apenas para descobrir que na segurança pública do Rio de Janeiro nada é o que parece. O sistema se reinventa e descobre como lucrar sem o intermédio do tráfico. Em perseguição ao caminho trilhado pelo sistema, Nascimento vai além dos limites do quartel, revelando as ligações das milícias com o Estado. E o preço por essa descoberta é alto: o inimigo agora é outro."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"엘리트 스쿼드 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"브라질의 S.W.A.T팀으로 불리는 ‘보피’부대는 브라질 최악의 갱들만을 수감하는 감옥 ‘반구 원’에서 폭동이 발생하자 이를 진압하기 위해 곧바로 투입된다. ‘보피’의 팀장인 ‘나시멘투’ 대령은 대원들을 감옥 주요 진입로에 배치시키고 작전을 지휘한다. 그러나 인권문제로 인한 후폭풍이 두려운 나머지 정부는 진압 명령을 내리지 않고 ‘보피’를 대기시킨다. 이 때, 인권협회장인 ‘프라가’가 사건의 원만한 해결을 위해‘반구 원’ 감옥에 도착하고 폭동의 주동자인 ‘베이라다’와 협상을 벌인다. 협상의 내용은 인질로 잡혀 있는 교도관 2명을 풀어주면 사건을 원하는 방향으로 정리해 주겠다는 것. 이에 ‘베이라다’가 인질 2명을 풀어주는 순간 ‘나시멘투’의 대기 명령을 어긴 ‘마티아즈’ 대위의 발포로 ‘베이라다’가 총에 맞아 즉사하고 폭동은 진압된다. 그러나 이 장면을 목격한 인권협회장 ‘프라가’는 현장의 모든 일을 언론에 폭로하게 되고, 이 사건으로 인해 ‘나시멘투’를 징계하자는 의견이 인권협회와 좌파 정치인 사이에 대두 되지만 국민들은 악랄한 갱단의 두목이 제거된 것에 환호하며 오히려 ‘나시멘투’를 지지하는 목소리가 높아진다. 이에 정부는 ‘나시멘투’를 ‘보피’부대 사령관에서 보직 해임하는 대신 정보부 차관으로 승진 발령시켜 사태 진압에 나서는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Елитен отряд 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Елитният отряд е доказал способностите си в ефективната борба с наркокартелите, като е отрязал пътищата на организираната престъпност и е разгромил няколко банди. Но сега, съвършено неочаквано, силите за сигурност започват да търпят поредица от поражения. Ще успеят ли да се съберат и да противостоят на кризисните проблеми?"},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"Tropa de Élite 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nascimento (Wagner Moura) se enfrenta a las milicias, un nuevo problema que ha plagado a Río de Janeiro. No tarda en tener enfrentamientos con el sistema que controla el estado, el equilibrio entre el reto de pacificar la ciudad y hacerse cargo de Rafael (Peter Van Held), su hijo adolescente, y Rosane (Maria Ribeiro), su ex esposa. A su lado cuenta con el apoyo de Matías (André Ramiro), elegido para sustituirle en el BOPE."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Biệt Đội Tinh Nhuệ 2: Kẻ Thù Bên Trong","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Tropa De Elite là xã hội thu nhỏ của thành phố Rio de Janeiro với những mặt tối tiêu cực, đầy rẫy tham nhũng, bạo lực, tội ác và nhấn mạnh, khai thác sâu bức tranh thối nát ngay chính lực lượng đại diện cho công lý - đội đặc nhiệm của cảnh sát chống tệ nạn buôn bán ma túy. Một số nhà bình luận cho rằng, bộ phim đã lột tả được một thực tế của ngành cảnh sát là những nhân viên trong lực lượng an ninh cũng phải thỏa hiệp để tồn tại..."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"精銳部隊2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在《精英部隊1》的故事結束3年後，《精英部隊 2》中巴西裡約特別警察行動部隊隊長納西門托的個人和家庭生活成為了續集篇的主綫。裡約特別警察在平復一次監獄暴動的行動中吃了大虧，傷及元氣，盡管擔當隊長之職的納西門托仕途平步青雲，但也因為這次事件的影響受到了牽連。與此同時，一場大規模的政治鬥爭在巴西的土地上燃燒開來，上至總統貴族，下至販夫走卒，警察局、軍隊和特別警察部門，統統捲入其中，一時間，一場喋血的槍殺事件火爆上演。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"精鋭暴隊 2：內鬼","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"精鋭部隊隊長納西文杜掃毒有功被拔擢轉任文職，但罪案之城裏約熱內盧貧民區依然毒案猖獗。納西文杜發現政府權力核心內藏販毒集團，兒子被牽聯受傷，令他再次披上武裝到街頭火拼…"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"エリート・スクワッド ブラジル特殊部隊BOPE","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Elitinis būrys 2: Priešas viduje","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Antroji dalis braziliško kriminalinio veiksmo filmo apie nusikaltėlių ir policijos kovą.  Po kruvino specialiųjų policijos operacijų būrio įsiveržimo į aukšto saugumo kalėjimą Rio Deženeire komandos pulkininkas ir kapitonas apkaltinami žmogaus teisių pažeidimu. Abu vyrai perkeliami dirbti į kitas darbo vietas."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Елітний загін 2: Ворог серед нас","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Елітний загін показав себе досить ефективним засобом боротьби з наркокартелями, перекривши кисень організованій злочинності та розгромивши кілька банд. Але тут зовсім несподівано сили правопорядку починають терпіти одну поразку за іншою."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"Elitná jednotka 2: Vnútorný nepriateľ","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Nascimento, veliteľ policajnej jednotky BOPE v Rio de Janeiro, krvavo potlačí vzburu vo väznici pre nebezpečných zločincov. Je zbavený svojej funkcie, i keď sa mu podarilo vyhnať z mestských slumov väčšinu drogových dealerov. Ich miesta však zaberá skorumpovaná polícia a Nascimento sa rozhodne zasiahnuť."},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"หลังจากมีการบุกโจมตี BOPE อย่างนองเลือดในเรือนจำ Bangu 1 ซึ่งเป็นเรือนจำที่มีความปลอดภัยสูงในเมืองริโอเดอจาเนโร เพื่อควบคุมการก่อกบฏของนักฝึกงาน พันโท Roberto Nascimento และกัปตัน André Matias ผู้บังคับบัญชาลำดับที่สอง ถูก Diogo Fraga สมาชิกองค์กร Human Right Aids กล่าวหาว่าประหารชีวิตนักโทษ Matias ถูกโอนไปยังกองตำรวจทหารที่ทุจริต และ Nascimento ได้รับการปลดปล่อยจาก BOPE โดยผู้ว่าการ"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Елитна јединица 2","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"После нереда у затвору током којих је било погинулих, некадашњи капетан Наскименто, сада високи официр за безбедност у Рио де Жанеиру, увучен је у политички сукоб у који су умешани представници владе и паравојних група. Ситуација у фавелама се мења и привидно стање стабилности постаје угрожено како се појачава полицијска бруталност."},"name":"Srpski","iso_639_1":"sr","iso_3166_1":"RS","english_name":"Serbian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"561272d09251410d80007645","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/561272d09251410d80007645","author":"Andres Gomez","content":"This second part has a better plot than the previous one but, other than that, more violence without much sense.","created_at":"2015-10-05T12:53:36.675Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:37.631Z","author_details":{"name":"Andres Gomez","rating":7,"username":"tanty","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"675503b60982b4626789f59a","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/675503b60982b4626789f59a","author":"Abrazilliancheeze","content":"**Bad in practice, ideal idea**\r\n\r\nThe second movie is boring. I like the first movie better, it has drama more quick. In this movie, you don't get the \"something bad is about to happen\" feeling. The movie is more focused on politics with not much violence. But it has a better plot. Watch the first movie then watch this second movie, It will make it more enjoyable","created_at":"2024-12-08T02:25:58.744Z","updated_at":"2024-12-16T16:46:05.507Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":null,"username":"Abrazilliancheeze","avatar_path":null}}],"recommendations":[{"id":7347,"adult":false,"title":"Elite Squad","video":false,"overview":"In 1997, before the visit of the pope to Rio de Janeiro, Captain Nascimento from BOPE (Special Police Operations Battalion) is assigned to eliminate the risks of the drug dealers in a dangerous slum nearby where the pope intends to be lodged.","genre_ids":[18,28,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.6477,"vote_count":2631,"poster_path":"/lwIXz785N2fXi8hsBr1IXciFlkM.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-05","vote_average":8.062,"backdrop_path":"/huUgrGkCetYSkDl5fMvZCXCbFKl.jpg","original_title":"Tropa de Elite","original_language":"pt"},{"id":8440,"adult":false,"title":"Carandiru","video":false,"overview":"When a doctor decides to carry out an AIDS prevention program inside Latin America’s largest prison: the Casa de Detenção de São Paulo - Carandiru, he meets the future victims of one of the darkest days in Brazilian History when the State of São Paulo’s Military Police, with the excuse for law enforcement, shot to death 111 people. Based on real facts and on the book written by Dráuzio Varella.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1432,"vote_count":594,"poster_path":"/kKAgIMwQWQ6u4s0c56XKSDX3vAs.jpg","release_date":"2003-03-21","vote_average":7.577,"backdrop_path":"/rhrBU761a5B4w7hhpA9og3fNBCH.jpg","original_title":"Carandiru","original_language":"pt"},{"id":20268,"adult":false,"title":"Last Stop 174","video":false,"overview":"Sandro was a boy who loved to sing rap, to kiss, to stare the statue of Christ the Redeemer and dreamed to go visit Copacabana. Growing up on streets, the story culminates at the infamous episode of 12th June 2000, when Sandro hijacked bus 174.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.485,"vote_count":187,"poster_path":"/qvSZA7HIJMelYSaQ7ObBCylDnsX.jpg","release_date":"2008-10-24","vote_average":7.195,"backdrop_path":"/xhK1B9ilRCvOKdEs6JofFQj5JDf.jpg","original_title":"Última Parada 174","original_language":"pt"},{"id":37817,"adult":false,"title":"Ó Paí, Ó: Look at This","video":false,"overview":"During the Carnival in the historical site of Pelourinho, Salvador da Bahia, we follow the lives of the tenants of a falling-to-pieces tenement house who try to get by using creativity, irony, humor, and music.","genre_ids":[10402,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4817,"vote_count":198,"poster_path":"/BFVGUEQxhORXLRsclpzvGsIIFY.jpg","release_date":"2007-03-30","vote_average":6.955,"backdrop_path":"/aQtgaQ4nOIKaPtbyqLLQs94DRvZ.jpg","original_title":"Ó Paí, Ó","original_language":"pt"},{"id":40096,"adult":false,"title":"A Dog's Will","video":false,"overview":"The lively João Grilo and the sly Chicó are poor guys living in the hinterland who cheat a bunch of people in a small town in Northeastern Brazil. When they die, they have to be judged by Christ, the Devil and the Virgin Mary before they are admitted to paradise.","genre_ids":[35,18,14,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.358,"vote_count":1203,"poster_path":"/ctfNJw6gofTjQvhOZeH8QKt0O2x.jpg","release_date":"2000-09-15","vote_average":8.4,"backdrop_path":"/alQqTpmEkxSLgajfEYTsTH6nAKB.jpg","original_title":"O Auto da Compadecida","original_language":"pt"},{"id":598,"adult":false,"title":"City of God","video":false,"overview":"In the poverty-stricken favelas of Rio de Janeiro in the 1970s, two young men choose different paths. Rocket is a budding photographer who documents the increasing drug-related violence of his neighborhood, while José “Zé” Pequeno is an ambitious drug dealer diving into a dangerous life of crime.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.1472,"vote_count":8021,"poster_path":"/k7eYdWvhYQyRQoU2TB2A2Xu2TfD.jpg","release_date":"2002-08-30","vote_average":8.427,"backdrop_path":"/uvitbjFU4JqvMwIkMWHp69bmUzG.jpg","original_title":"Cidade de Deus","original_language":"pt"},{"id":73624,"adult":false,"title":"The Man from the Future","video":false,"overview":"Zero is a brilliant scientist. However, 20 years ago, he was publicly humiliated when he lost Helena, the love of his life. One day, an accidental experience with one of his inventions causes him to travel back in time to 1991. Having taken the opportunity to change history, Zero returns to own time to find totally changed.","genre_ids":[35,14,878,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.307,"vote_count":382,"poster_path":"/cWfdBMbe3SodE14h3VptXy6sQZm.jpg","release_date":"2011-09-02","vote_average":7.219,"backdrop_path":"/hel4RhpqHWamrfCueE7TZMEWJ5c.jpg","original_title":"O Homem do Futuro","original_language":"pt"},{"id":52345,"adult":false,"title":"Lisbela and the Prisoner","video":false,"overview":"Lisbela is a young woman who loves going to the movies. Leléu is a con man, going from town to town selling all sort of things and performing as master of ceremonies for some cheesy numbers, such as the woman who gets transformed into a gorilla. He gets involved with Linaura, a sexy and beautiful woman who happens to be the wife of the most frightening hitman of the place. The hitman finds out his wife's affair and goes after Leléu, who has to leave in a hurry. In another town, he meets and falls instantly in love with Lisbela, who is engaged to Douglas, a hillbilly who tries hard to pass for a cosmopolitan Rio de Janeiro dweller.","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6118,"vote_count":402,"poster_path":"/raCdo5Hjpd3uXbpSd1JZ7tEyE31.jpg","release_date":"2003-08-22","vote_average":7.826,"backdrop_path":"/eAOOeqa14oCxgdKxLvpDYxCJhqQ.jpg","original_title":"Lisbela e o Prisioneiro","original_language":"pt"},{"id":58857,"adult":false,"title":"13 Assassins","video":false,"overview":"A bravado period action film set at the end of Japan's feudal era in which a group of unemployed samurai are enlisted to bring down a sadistic lord and prevent him from ascending to the throne and plunging the country into a war-torn future.","genre_ids":[12,18,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.2556,"vote_count":1231,"poster_path":"/yUsVsiVXUwClk4vSCx80vrdO6MV.jpg","release_date":"2010-09-25","vote_average":7.327,"backdrop_path":"/A3Jl4Vu2Xx4J9hWWKX1xO6NOeV4.jpg","original_title":"十三人の刺客","original_language":"ja"},{"id":377273,"adult":false,"title":"Aquarius","video":false,"overview":"Clara, a vibrant former music critic and widow with flowing tresses is the only remaining apartment owner in a beautiful older building targeted for demolition by ruthless luxury high-rise developers. Clara proves to be a force to be reckoned with as she thwarts the builders plans to kick her out of the apartment.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.3108,"vote_count":496,"poster_path":"/9hwkjmtl3HCXe7JW2BVSyjLXHCo.jpg","release_date":"2016-09-01","vote_average":7.448,"backdrop_path":"/veZzmysk4x3clDOsXiAADWVjL40.jpg","original_title":"Aquarius","original_language":"pt"},{"id":177221,"adult":false,"title":"The Battery","video":false,"overview":"In rural Connecticut, baseball players Ben and Mickey are trying to survive a zombie plague. They are forced to form a battery: a catcher and a pitcher who work together to outwit the batter, the one who hits the ball. And the batter in this case just happens to be a zombie. Tough Ben and gentle Mickey frequently disagree on the best way to go about the situation. Then they suddenly hear a human voice through their walkie-talkies. Is salvation nearby, like Mickey thinks, or is Ben’s suspicion justified?","genre_ids":[18,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.819,"vote_count":299,"poster_path":"/nI7lzx2t4UPfuqhunB5bEVymOOV.jpg","release_date":"2012-10-13","vote_average":6.134,"backdrop_path":"/tgA2GbzyUBVm13qvI7AyPIdWSsS.jpg","original_title":"The Battery","original_language":"en"},{"id":63493,"adult":false,"title":"The Ledge","video":false,"overview":"A thriller in which a battle of philosophies between a fundamentalist Christian and an atheist escalates into a lethal battle of wills.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0723,"vote_count":378,"poster_path":"/cTaDS6CTIfZ5MH189ub6oE1FATk.jpg","release_date":"2011-05-06","vote_average":6.168,"backdrop_path":"/fWOfr0L1ISpP3KF8qY2qG1qrxMi.jpg","original_title":"The Ledge","original_language":"en"},{"id":560491,"adult":false,"title":"Ghost Killers vs. Bloody Mary","video":false,"overview":"A group of three youtubers who call themselves experts in supernatural beings decide to win public recognition once and for all. For this they plot a plan to capture a being known to all. It is the spirit of a light-haired woman who died in an unknown way and who haunts the bathrooms of schools across the country: the blonde in the bathroom.","genre_ids":[27,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3668,"vote_count":126,"poster_path":"/jXChjh6YQFNDH5mUd0A2Fs7DjFE.jpg","release_date":"2018-11-29","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/cyAiY7pBfkEwzL5EVIxCDTNE1eK.jpg","original_title":"Exterminadores do Além Contra a Loira do Banheiro","original_language":"pt"},{"id":360139,"adult":false,"title":"Elis","video":false,"overview":"The film tells the story of the energetic and pulsating singer Elis Regina since her arrival in Rio de Janeiro at age 19 until her tragic and early death. Despite all the difficulties, success comes fulminant and the life of Elis Regina gained national and international recognition, becoming undoubtedly considered today the greatest Brazilian singer of all time.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4424,"vote_count":124,"poster_path":"/cf55SD27tKBrYMRqyfQ2LDeNyKs.jpg","release_date":"2016-11-24","vote_average":7.21,"backdrop_path":"/b1pzSJI1QSs7jRfXK7qs9wVxqTi.jpg","original_title":"Elis","original_language":"pt"},{"id":36093,"adult":false,"title":"Behind the Sun","video":false,"overview":"Brazilian badlands, April 1910. Tonho is ordered by his father to avenge the death of his older brother. The young man knows that if he commits this crime, his life will be divided in two: the twenty years he has already lived and the few days he has left to live, before the other family avenges their son's death. He is torn between fulfilling his ancestral duty and rebelling against it, urged by his younger brother Pacu. That's when a tiny travelling circus passes through the vast badlands where Tonho's family lives.","genre_ids":[18,53,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4076,"vote_count":129,"poster_path":"/zkNQBhT8op04I1JYwRqNhjX4quD.jpg","release_date":"2001-12-12","vote_average":7.333,"backdrop_path":"/9fKYqsnqDKvu2vRgTzJMTfPeBoc.jpg","original_title":"Abril Despedaçado","original_language":"pt"},{"id":511404,"adult":false,"title":"The Summer House","video":false,"overview":"A large and beautiful property on the French Riviera. A place that seems out of time and sheltered from the rest of the world. Anna goes there with her daughter for a few days of vacation. Amidst her family, friends and the house staff, Anna has to handle her fresh break-up with her partner and the writing of her next film.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.2287,"vote_count":91,"poster_path":"/srneCbN2ymaYo6DYEcFLBkrb9ev.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-01","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":"/nYjCcu5oxLNwBdgm4SxdL8RdyEx.jpg","original_title":"Les Estivants","original_language":"fr"},{"id":21625,"adult":false,"title":"Gulaal","video":false,"overview":"A law student witnesses the struggles of the Rajputs, deception, homicide and crime after being elected as General Secretary of his college.","genre_ids":[80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5622,"vote_count":66,"poster_path":"/2FT2A8qh3nbqqCLgpkXhPBCVW42.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-13","vote_average":6.758,"backdrop_path":"/r9fwjoJOYT1xQGHwLkSJA6snhsR.jpg","original_title":"गुलाल","original_language":"hi"},{"id":23854,"adult":false,"title":"The Assailant","video":false,"overview":"Based on the life 